HOME_WHAT_IS_DIAMOND_TITLE=What is Diamond?|Is it really the future of the web?
HOME_WHAT_IS_DIAMOND_CONTENT:
Diamond is a <b>FREE open-source</b> full-stack web-framework written in <b>The D Programming Language</b>.
<br><br>
It's inspired by <b>ASP.NET</b> and uses <b>vibe.d</b> for its backend, making Diamond a very powerful framework.
<br><br>
It builds on modern practices for both web-frontend and web-backends and it's not limited to a single environment.
<br><br>
Diamond is able to run on the most popular operating systems, platforms and under popular environments.
;

