HOME_I18N_TITLE=Localization &amp; Internationalization|Without complexity or code duplication
HOME_I18N_CONTENT:
The internet is a place where people from all over the world meet, but sometimes it's great to support the locales from specific contries, cultures etc.<br>
<br>
Diamond has an easy-to-use localization and internationalization API built-in, which you can combine with specialized view-syntaxes to rapidly develop multi-language solutions.
;

HOME_EU_COOKIE_TITLE=Law &amp; Standard Compliant|Follows standards by ex. EU for cookies, GDPR etc.
HOME_EU_COOKIE_CONTENT:
It's important for professional business to be compliant with laws and regulations.<br>
<br>
By using Diamond you get a lot of helpful functionality and tools that can help you comply with these.<br>
<br>
Diamond has support for cookie-consent and various GDPR helper functionality.<br>
<br>
All implementations can be bend and configured to match your exact needs.
;

HOME_TEST_DRIVEN_DEV_TITLE=Test-Driven Development|Testing is essential for professional solutions
HOME_TEST_DRIVEN_DEV_CONTENT:
Diamond has support for D's built-in unittesting, but also has a more advanced unittesting API.<br>
<br>
Diamond's own unittesting API can be shaped to test certain requests and target specific areas of the application.<br>
<br>
This is useful, because you can do real HTTP tests without a browser or third-party tools.
;

